Chef-In-Box offers Halal-certified bento meals in a wide variety of local and international flavours. 
They are delivered frozen and take only minutes to heat at home.
These ready-to-eat meals make use of advanced cook-chill and cook-freeze technology to seal in the nutrients. 
They also contain no added preservatives, additives or artificial flavorings, making them more nutritious than alternative quick meal solutions.
.
Perfect meal for this coming Ramadan with your own household family :) .
